datastore-services-ng (1.0) trusty; urgency=medium

  * datastore-ng implements all features of obsolete monolithic
    datastore package ... and beyond
  * datastore-server class is now plugable. Plugins replace old
    'namespace' parameter, defining a new syntax to invoke methods:
    server.PLUGIN_NAME.method()
  * Plugins also allow to extend datastore functionality with new methods.

 -- Luis Antonio Garcia Gisbert <luisgg@gmail.com>  Thu, 16 Jul 2015 17:45:44 +0200

